# Architecture Overview

ASTRA FourWard is a forward-only ledger design with these major components:

1. Deterministic state engine
2. Witness aggregation layer
3. Prime discovery engine
4. Merkle Star Map
5. Canon selection layer
6. Verification and testing harness

The protocol concept uses multi-domain witness inputs to make history harder to falsify quietly.

